  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord server</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Travel around the steppes of the Great North with your truck. Pay attention to its condition and gas level, and choose the best route. Will you manage to get your truck to its destination without succumbing to the dangers of this hostile land?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/5b42914249ddea320aa32d3f79da3e2e.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your adventure will vary according to your decisions…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Experience a short but richly layered narrative.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Make various choices</strong> with many risky obstacles and useful resources.<br></li><li>Meet around <strong>twenty colorful characters.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/7b3eb5fae9072df4ef08733d870b521b.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The more you care about your resources, the more peaceful your progress will be!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Manage your resources</strong> to progress smoothly.<br></li><li>Keep a close eye on <strong>your gas level, truck condition, and money</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Collect these resources</strong> as you visit different places on the map.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/8b2ccc06b8e8241f876aa0f758aec30d.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dive into an original universe, inspired by Slavic legendary figures…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore picturesque landscapes</strong> depicting the magic of the country throughout the map.<br></li><li><strong>Discover the Slavic folklore</strong> behind FibreTigre’s writing (<i>Out There</i>, <i>Game of Rôles</i>).<br></li><li>The <strong>hand-drawn art style</strong> of Quentin Vijoux will immerse you even more in the universe.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Travel around the steppes of the Great North with your truck. Pay attention to its condition and gas level, and choose the best route. Will you manage to get your truck to its destination without succumbing to the dangers of this hostile land?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/5b42914249ddea320aa32d3f79da3e2e.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/443714a81bec85456a848d0d403465b1.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your adventure will vary according to your decisions…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Experience a short but richly layered narrative.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Make various choices</strong> with many risky obstacles and useful resources.<br></li><li>Meet around <strong>twenty colorful characters.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/7b3eb5fae9072df4ef08733d870b521b.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/07bf95aa3bf637a024cd4d7b06615009.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The more you care about your resources, the more peaceful your progress will be!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Manage your resources</strong> to progress smoothly.<br></li><li>Keep a close eye on <strong>your gas level, truck condition, and money</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Collect these resources</strong> as you visit different places on the map.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/8b2ccc06b8e8241f876aa0f758aec30d.avif?t=1707207281\" width=601 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.poster.avif?t=1707207281\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.webm?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633860/extras/f241dcb2ce67835ee6c1f33e74b4d4bf.mp4?t=1707207281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dive into an original universe, inspired by Slavic legendary figures…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore picturesque landscapes</strong> depicting the magic of the country throughout the map.<br></li><li><strong>Discover the Slavic folklore</strong> behind FibreTigre’s writing (<i>Out There</i>, <i>Game of Rôles</i>).<br></li><li>The <strong>hand-drawn art style</strong> of Quentin Vijoux will immerse you even more in the universe.</li></ul>",
